  <brief_title>Effectiveness of Cane in Osteoarthritis (OA) Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Impact of Daily Cane Use on Pain, Function, Quality of Life and Energy Consumption During the Gait in Patients With Knee Osteoarthritis</official_title>
